      "sha256": "7efb9e99e991dde0836a5bdbcda672fb0513de6bed0517cada0ef7f7863ebf27",
      "source_region": "div.problem-additional-text",
      "text": "[Ri76] Richter, Bernd, \\\"{U}ber die Monotonie von Differenzenfolgen. Acta Arith. (1976), 225-227."
    },
    "remarks": {
      "sha256": "e1236d502624b569e000e4849cd0bceb377fe9fbbd5bb4c0ab3c878c0e26111a",
      "source_region": "div.problem-additional-text",
      "text": "Richter \\cite{Ri76} proved that\\[\\liminf_n \\frac{q_n}{n^2}>0.352\\cdots.\\]"
    },
    "statement": {
      "sha256": "64657090a58ba486462ac5563f0108f0d8ad2beba72ccfb1552f1521684af52c",
      "source_region": "div#content",
      "text": "Let $q_1<q_2<\\cdots$ be a sequence of primes such that\\[q_{n+1}-q_n\\geq q_n-q_{n-1}.\\]Must\\[\\lim_n \\frac{q_n}{n^2}=\\infty?\\]"
    }
  },
